1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg>Encrypted Inquiry</button></a><a href="/contact"><button type="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 transition-colors h-8 px-3 text-xs rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground border border-primary-border hover:bg-primary/90 shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:shadow-xl" aria-label="Get a Quote"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-phone w-4 h-4"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>Get a Quote</button></a></div><button id="mobile-menu-toggle" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobile-menu" class="md:hidden p-2 text-slate-600" aria-label="Toggle menu"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-menu w-6 h-6"><line x1="4" x2="20" y1="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="4" x2="20" y1="6" y2="6"></line><line x1="4" x2="20" y1="18" y2="18"></line></svg></button></div><div id="mobile-menu" class="md:hidden hidden border-t border-slate-200 bg-white" aria-hidden="true"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex flex-col gap-3"><a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Home</a><a href="/services" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Services</a><a href="/about" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">About</a><a href="/blog" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Field Notes</a><a href="/contact" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 hover:text-primary py-2">Contact</a><a href="/contact" class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium rounded-md border border-emerald-500/50 text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-50 min-h-8 px-3 text-xs py-2">Encrypted Inquiry</a><a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground min-h-8 px-3 text-xs py-2">Get a Quote</a></div></div></nav><main class="flex-grow"><section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-44 md:pb-24 overflow-hidden bg-slate-50"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div><div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-primary/5 to-transparent skew-x-12 transform origin-top-right translate-x-32"></div><div class="container relative mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 z-10 max-w-4xl"><span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-semibold text-sm mb-6 border border-primary/20 animate-fade-in-up">For clients + collaborators</span><h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-[1.1] mb-6 animate-fade-in-up delay-1">Feedback + <span class="text-primary">testimonial.</span></h1><p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-4 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed animate-fade-in-up delay-2">If you've worked with PlausiDen, your feedback shapes what we ship next. The first section is for any feedback; the second section is the optional testimonial questions if you're willing to be quoted. We read every response by hand. Nothing here is shared without your consent.</p></div></section><section class="py-12 bg-white text-slate-900"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 max-w-2xl"><form method="post" action="/feedback" class="space-y-10"><div class="space-y-4"><h2 class="font-display font-bold leading-tight text-xl text-slate-900">Who you are</h2><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-name">Your name</label><input type="text" id="fb-name" name="name" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm h-12 bg-slate-50" placeholder="Your name" maxlength="100" required></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-company">Company / organization</label><input type="text" id="fb-company" name="company" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm h-12 bg-slate-50" placeholder="Optional" maxlength="200"></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-email">Email (for follow-up)</label><input type="email" id="fb-email" name="email" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm h-12 bg-slate-50" placeholder="Optional" maxlength="200"></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><h2 class="font-display font-bold leading-tight text-xl text-slate-900">General feedback</h2><p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Anything you want us to know. Keep it short, keep it honest. One sentence is fine.</p><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-worked">1. What worked well?</label><textarea id="fb-worked" name="worked_well" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm min-h-[150px] bg-slate-50 resize-none" maxlength="2000"></textarea></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-didnt">2. What didn't?</label><textarea id="fb-didnt" name="didnt_work" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm min-h-[150px] bg-slate-50 resize-none" maxlength="2000"></textarea></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><h2 class="font-display font-bold leading-tight text-xl text-slate-900">Testimonial (optional)</h2><p class="text-sm text-slate-500">If you're willing to be quoted on our site, answer as many of these as you'd like. Short and honest beats long and tidy. We'll edit for length, never for voice — and we won't publish anything without your sign-off.</p><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-consent">3. How can we attribute you?</label><select id="fb-consent" name="consent" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm h-12 bg-slate-50"><option value="">Pick one</option><option value="full">Use my name and company</option><option value="name_only">Use my name, no company</option><option value="role_only">Use my role + industry, no name</option><option value="anonymous">Anonymous (&quot;client in the legal sector&quot;)</option><option value="private">Don't publish — feedback only</option></select></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-alt">4. Before working with PlausiDen, what was the alternative? What would you have done?</label><textarea id="fb-alt" name="alternative" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm min-h-[150px] bg-slate-50 resize-none" maxlength="2000"></textarea></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-why">5. What made you decide to work with us instead?</label><textarea id="fb-why" name="why_chose" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm min-h-[150px] bg-slate-50 resize-none" maxlength="2000"></textarea></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-changed">6. What does the working system let you do now that you couldn't before?</label><textarea id="fb-changed" name="whats_changed" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm min-h-[150px] bg-slate-50 resize-none" maxlength="2000"></textarea></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-rec">7. If a peer asked you whether to engage PlausiDen for similar work, what would you tell them?</label><textarea id="fb-rec" name="recommend" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm min-h-[150px] bg-slate-50 resize-none" maxlength="2000"></textarea></div><div class="space-y-2"><label class="text-sm font-medium leading-none" for="fb-extra">8. Anything else?</label><textarea id="fb-extra" name="anything_else" class="flex w-full rounded-md border border-input px-3 py-2 text-base ring-offset-background focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 md:text-sm min-h-[150px] bg-slate-50 resize-none" maxlength="2000"></textarea></div></div><div class="pt-4"><button type="submit" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 transition-colors h-12 px-8 py-6 text-lg rounded-xl bg-primary text-primary-foreground border border-primary-border hover:bg-primary/90 shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 hover:shadow-xl" aria-label="Send feedback">Send feedback</button><div class="mt-3"><p class="text-xs text-slate-500">We'll read it. If you flagged a quote we can use, we'll email you the proposed wording before anything goes live.</p></div></div></form></div></section></main><footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 py-16"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12"><div class="space-y-6"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white"><div class="bg-primary p-1.5 rounded-lg"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-6 h-6 text-white"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"/></svg></div><span class="font-display font-bold text-xl tracking-tight">PlausiDen <span class="text-primary">LLC</span></span></div><p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs">Providing comprehensive, high-quality IT solutions that empower modern enterprises. General yet specific excellence in technology.</p></div><div class="space-y-6"><h3 class="text-white font-display font-semibold text-lg">Company</h3><ul class="space-y-3"><li><a href="/"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Home</span></a></li><li><a href="/about"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">About Us</span></a></li><li><a href="/services"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Services</span></a></li><li><a href="/capabilities"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Capabilities</span></a></li><li><a href="/case-studies"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Case Studies</span></a></li><li><a href="/blog"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Field Notes</span></a></li><li><a href="/how-we-work"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">How We Work</span></a></li><li><a href="/pricing-transparency"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Pricing</span></a></li><li><a href="/contact"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Contact</span></a></li><li><a href="/feedback"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Feedback</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="space-y-6"><h3 class="text-white font-display font-semibold text-lg">Solutions</h3><ul class="space-y-3"><li><a href="/solutions/legal"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Legal</span></a></li><li><a href="/solutions/healthcare"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Healthcare</span></a></li><li><a href="/solutions/journalism"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Journalism</span></a></li><li><a href="/solutions/financial-advisors"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Financial Advisors</span></a></li><li><a href="/solutions/nonprofit"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Nonprofits</span></a></li><li class="text-sm">IT Operations</li><li class="text-sm">Cyber Security</li></ul></div><div class="space-y-6"><h3 class="text-white font-display font-semibold text-lg">Contact</h3><ul class="space-y-3 space-y-4"><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg><a href="tel:9783516495"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">978-351-6495</span></a></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg><a href="mailto:team@plausiden.com"><span class="text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors">team@plausiden.com</span></a></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary shrink-0 mt-0.5"><path d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg><span class="text-sm">Massachusetts, USA</span></li></ul></div></div><div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-slate-500"><p>© PlausiDen LLC. All rights reserved.</p><div class="flex gap-6"><a href="/privacy-directive"><span class="hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Sovereign Privacy Directive</span></a><a href="/terms-of-service"><span class="hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer">Sovereign Terms of Service</span></a></div></div></div></footer></div></div></body></html>
